## Summary
This documentation details the integration between Amplitude and TheTradeDesk, allowing advertisers to send user cohorts for targeted advertising campaigns with a 30-day TTL for users. The integration requires mapping identifiers to TheTradeDesk's GUID, raw device GUID, or Unified ID 2.0, and includes setup instructions for both platforms.

